name: NEO YC 114: Africa's Finest
description: One of twenty-seven different cards created for the first ever New Eden Open tournament of YC 114. While not the first ever capsuleer tournament it was the first of its kind to be sponsored by a private media organization and broadcast to a much broader audience. It was also set a new benchmark for prizes in a capsuleer tournament. The New Eden Open broke the tradition of previous capsuleer tournaments by allowing teams to form at will, without the need to be bound to the same alliance.
